                        <condition key="good">The leather cover is for the most part missing.
                           Remnants of turn-ins and textile inlays are visible on the back board.
                           
 Some fols. have slightly damaged edges (esp. fols. 1 and 104).
                           f.1 has holes.
 Some fols. are stained with water and wax.
 Cuts
                           and tears carefully amended in fols. 6, 21, 37, 52, 86, 89.</condition>
